Ranger Help for: inspect
========================

SYNTAX:      inspect <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  hunting

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to carefully analyze an opponent, revealing
information about their stats, strengths, and weaknesses. A successful
inspection may reveal the target's approximate hit points, damage type
resistances, elemental vulnerabilities, and combat style. The amount
of detail revealed depends on the Ranger's skill level and intelligence.
This is an invaluable scouting tool for preparing to fight tough enemies.
